{"id": "1270980359995133995", "channel_id": "1269336432577613834", "type": 0, "author_id": "1226317601831911467", "author_name": "tranquil_monkey_73179", "author_bot": false, "content": "挽尊，准备关池了，建议能抽一个的都抽一个。现在每天玩奥尔拉真的好快乐，谁都能搭，比混沌24有乐趣多了。", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T05:42:11.496000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1269336432577613834", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "奥尔拉详解", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1174179755759763526"]}
