{"id": "1271059191271784489", "channel_id": "1271059191271784489", "type": 0, "author_id": "1122207553053528217", "author_name": "yi000607", "author_bot": false, "content": "遊玩143天\n第一次打到375分享給需要的朋朋\n順序從5-4打到1-4。\n5-4：超維24\n4-4：神父環拉\n3-4：尤烏羊媽\n2-4：鯊魚水母\n1-4：深海毒\n總共是2深海2血肉1超維\n\n5-4\n超維24好用得點在於道中可以過得非常舒服，但以這次Boss為N的情況，其實混沌24回更合適，不過我的環拉已經配給神父了所以也沒辦法\n4-4\n一階段羅坦的攻擊力非常低，就用蜘蛛慢慢疊戒備+神父慢慢磨，在一階段打命定的傷害撐起來，2階段我雙命定一回合斬殺，就算不能斬殺也能靠菲神死抗硬扛。\n3-4\n尤烏一定是能扛一關沒啥好說，不過我的練度很低，因此造物算是很好的情況下才順利過，有超限尤烏會更輕鬆\n2-4 1-4\n慢慢磨即可，我是有凹死抗才過，畢竟練度超低\n也能用深海盾或者利茲毒、希落打擊去打\nUID:100394120", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:55:26.337000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:59:01.420000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "♥️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1271059191670247494", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185449.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 103360, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059191670247494/Screenshot_20240808_185449.jpg?ex=69cba81e&is=69ca569e&hm=11770a237f5d817c2017e9b92b66a0f33555ad41f9d962c10d5104348644d347&"}, {"id": "1271059192114970695", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185452.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 102100, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059192114970695/Screenshot_20240808_185452.jpg?ex=69cba81e&is=69ca569e&hm=0e296d354190c04b2f0eba3b4569f8596bb16f23c6cb9bfbebe0448ed3a249d3&"}, {"id": "1271059192408707082", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185444.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 140760, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059192408707082/Screenshot_20240808_185444.jpg?ex=69cba81e&is=69ca569e&hm=28f889a0e5d70cad0dd1d508a701b77f93ec203a6a264ad21188aedf2030e7c5&"}, {"id": "1271059192718950410", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185435.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 144019, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059192718950410/Screenshot_20240808_185435.jpg?ex=69cba81e&is=69ca569e&hm=b4b5ad472ec5de382b5d72026d074f9a7feddf61cafb06f00ac806edebaceabd&"}, {"id": "1271059192953700403", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185429.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 143233, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059192953700403/Screenshot_20240808_185429.jpg?ex=69cba81e&is=69ca569e&hm=b3cf607178aaa8ba3c5326cf8454c4b95974bcba7eb19a85a2e3aff654188b16&"}, {"id": "1271059193264083045", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185423.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 142280, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059193264083045/Screenshot_20240808_185423.jpg?ex=69cba81e&is=69ca569e&hm=5a00ab0bee4fd11f60d768508259eee43bf479c67f56a3123f7bb06335d759af&"}, {"id": "1271059193654411344", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185418.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 141672, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059193654411344/Screenshot_20240808_185418.jpg?ex=69cba81e&is=69ca569e&hm=aeaa76a3e73252012d837a1f36fbfdb426f1cc05f28739c463ea6a9e5d08b4dc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1271059191271784489", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超低練度溶災375攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1181143392739147778", "1174179680056791130"]}
