{"id": "1271052437394030684", "channel_id": "1271052437394030684", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "本期打了純超維的融災375，~~都打了就想來曬一下~~，並提供一些超維在融災配對的思路和強度建議。\n\n首先我會盡量抓一個銀鑰位，一個生存位，並圍繞著主C的打法選擇配合的角色。\n\n而詩人在超維界域是非常強非常關鍵的角色，有了詩人的超維隊伍強度上升不只一個檔次，因此助戰借詩人。\n\n不過我在關卡選擇上出了些問題，導致打得比較艱難，換一下順序會好打很多，留言是詳細陣容。\n\n2024.8.8.mob\n\nUID:100352106", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:28:36.087000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:34:37.751000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1271052437691568128", "filename": "375_1.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 165699, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271052437394030684/1271052437691568128/375_1.JPG?ex=69cba1d4&is=69ca5054&hm=f3640d52166496ce14595472aed20ca8d32ba5b716c7f0bd4237148c70b3a612&"}, {"id": "1271052438106935328", "filename": "375_2.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 166772, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271052437394030684/1271052438106935328/375_2.JPG?ex=69cba1d4&is=69ca5054&hm=93ed8ad8604a20be21a7ef7509f049628eb8ef11ac56a02929cf87f13e04cae6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1271052437394030684", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超維融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179755759763526"]}
{"id": "1271052511360581664", "channel_id": "1271052437394030684", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:28:53.722000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1271052511503061083", "filename": "1bc5a69b4f256e87.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 228435, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271052437394030684/1271052511503061083/1bc5a69b4f256e87.JPG?ex=69cba1e5&is=69ca5065&hm=7304a122f7840261cbdd8e3c4c4e5993d06b0fc1934fb0437f731ba94a0aecb1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1271052437394030684", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超維融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179755759763526"]}
{"id": "1271052518788436048", "channel_id": "1271052437394030684", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "第五波由於擺而選擇用鼠鼠，是個不太好的決定，用單傷C如阿姨會好很多。平常沒在打融災，進去才發現N有反擊，導致得找生存造物才能過，凹了一陣子。\n道中由於鼠鼠配上珈崙、詩人的強度，基本滿血過，並凹了四張高衝進空間，打完後發現三張就夠了。\n常駐喜情緒，爆發時可以切一下其他情緒，但要找時間切回來。\n\n整體而言鼠鼠這隊在融災的強度很高，只是遇到反擊王相對不好打，但配上本期融災的第五關的擺，玩起來很爽，推薦去玩看看。", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:28:55.493000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1271052437394030684", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超維融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179755759763526"]}
