{"id": "1271052577575796757", "channel_id": "1271052437394030684", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:29:09.509000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1271052577148112988", "filename": "20f5e09eab521742.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 223901, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271052437394030684/1271052577148112988/20f5e09eab521742.JPG?ex=69cba1f5&is=69ca5075&hm=feb83bf2b6c09c52e44ca7db98b96550d3475f203f4a87446697f54470f04021&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1271052437394030684", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超維融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179755759763526"]}
{"id": "1271052591379517562", "channel_id": "1271052437394030684", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "第四波用莉茲，也不太好，主要在於莉茲更好處理第三關的艾爾瓦，但以本關而言莉茲過的蠻輕鬆。\n\n打法就是落地存三四張綠炎進空間，會吃一次症狀，每場戰鬥關卡進去就先爆發一波，打到剩一個小怪拖著，繼續存綠炎做空間，補狀態，不斷反覆打到王關。\n王關打法：存算 => 覺醒艾瑞卡 => 空間打艾瑞卡X疊力 => 配上莉茲狂氣爆發丟出綠炎打傷害。\n常駐喜情緒，爆發時可以切一下其他情緒，但要找時間切回來。\n\n有詩人、艾瑞卡的莉茲在融災強度也算高，主要生存差了一些，但通常也夠用。", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:29:12.800000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1271052437394030684", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超維融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179755759763526"]}
