{"id": "1271052804147908630", "channel_id": "1271052437394030684", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "第二波用燉雞，燉雞適合前兩關不會成長的王，慢慢磨。\n\n毫無反應，就只是個燉雞。帶潘好過道中，少吃一些症狀，同時也沒角色能放了。\n\n就只是個燉雞。", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:30:03.528000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1271052437394030684", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超維融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179755759763526"]}
